latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Remember that feeling of anticipation as you count down your days to your next trip? It’s time to reclaim that. With a wide range of cuisines to select from, finest rooms to snuggle in,  work-spaces to power through the day productively and relaxing spa sessions to enjoy on the weekend, The Shalimar Hotel is a home away from home! 

There has never been a better time to escape yet stay rooted in safety and care within your city. We are waiting for you! With new and improved standards of safety and hygiene, familiar warm smiles and a continuous effort in ensuring your stay is relaxed and delightful. Visit the link in our bio to book your ultimate staycation!
